headline: eBay (EBAY): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: eBay trades at $87.03 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, gaining 14.6% over the last six months. At the same time, the S&P 500 has returned 9.9%.
